articles.title: Asian Paints Q3: Net profit up 34% to Rs 1,475 crore, revenue up 5%; meets estimates - Moneycontrol
articles.description: The company witnessed 12 percent volume growth and 5.5 percent value sales in Decorative Business for India.
articles.content: Asian Paints on January 17 reported a consolidated net profit of Rs 1,475.16 crore for the third quarter of the financial year 2023-24, up 34.4 percent from Rs 1,097.06 crore in the year-ago period. … [+2791 chars]
